# System-level requirements
artifact SYS:
    attribute id is mandatory string
    attribute contents is mandatory string
    attribute title is mandatory string
    attribute priority is mandatory enum [critical, high, medium, low]
    attribute status is mandatory enum [draft, active, retired]
    attribute category is optional enum [performance, safety, interface, functional]
    attribute verified is optional boolean

# Software requirements
artifact REQ:
    attribute id is mandatory string
    attribute contents is mandatory string
    attribute title is mandatory string
    attribute parent is optional reference to parent
    attribute status is mandatory enum [draft, active, retired]
    attribute priority is mandatory enum [critical, high, medium, low]
    attribute verify is optional string
    attribute version is optional integer
    attribute tag is optional multiple string
    attribute related is optional multiple reference

trace from REQ to SYS is mandatory via commit
